            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cs-block cs-feature-image">
      <img src="/images/case-studies/casestudy-samar.png" alt="SAMAR Certification &amp; Assessment platform" loading="lazy" />
    </div>
    
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cs-single-col">
        <div>
          <div class="cs-block scope-v2">
            <div class="scope-v2-intro">
              <span class="scope-v2-eyebrow">Scope of Work</span>
              <h2 class="scope-v2-heading">What We Delivered</h2>
              <p class="scope-v2-lead">SAMAR was built around six integrated components &mdash; applicant portals, evaluator workflows, multi-level approval chains, digital certificate issuance, surveillance management, and operational dashboards &mdash; all running on a single digital backbone for QCI.</p>
            </div>
            <ol class="scope-v2-timeline">
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">01.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Online Application &amp; Document Management</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Self-service applicant portal for organisations to submit certification applications, upload supporting documents, and track application status in real time.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Samar What we deliver image step1 .png" alt="Online application and document management screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">02.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Evaluator Assignment &amp; Management</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Automated and manual evaluator assignment system &mdash; matching assessors to applications based on domain expertise, availability, and conflict-of-interest rules.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Samar What we deliver image step2 .png" alt="Evaluator assignment and management screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">03.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Multi-Level Approval Workflow</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Configurable multi-stage approval workflow &mdash; technical review, committee review, and final approval stages &mdash; with role-based access and full audit trail on every decision.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Samar What we deliver image step3 .png" alt="Multi-level approval workflow screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">04.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Digital Certificate Issuance</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Automated generation and issuance of digitally signed certificates upon approval &mdash; with QR code verification and public certificate validation portal.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Samar What we deliver image step4 .png" alt="Digital certificate issuance screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">05.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Surveillance &amp; Renewal Management</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Periodic surveillance visit scheduling, renewal reminder workflows, and compliance monitoring for active certificate holders.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Samar What we deliver image step5 .png" alt="Surveillance and renewal management screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="scope-v2-item">
                <div class="scope-v2-num">06.</div>
                <h3 class="scope-v2-title">Reporting &amp; Analytics Dashboard</h3>
                <p class="scope-v2-desc">Operational dashboard for QCI management &mdash; application volumes, approval turnaround times, evaluator performance, and certificate status across all schemes.</p>
                <div class="scope-v2-media">
                  <img src="/images/logos/gov/Samar What we deliver image step6 .png" alt="Reporting and analytics dashboard screens" loading="lazy" />
                </div>
              </li>
            </ol>
          </div>
          
          <section class="impact-metrics">
            <h2 class="impact-metrics-heading">Impact Metrics</h2>
            <p class="impact-metrics-lead">Real results from organisations that have digitised regulatory and certification workflows with our platforms.</p>
            <div class="impact-metrics-grid">
              <article class="impact-metric-card">
                <div class="impact-metric-num">E2E</div>
                <div class="impact-metric-lbl">Certification lifecycle digitised</div>
              </article>
              <article class="impact-metric-card">
                <div class="impact-metric-num">Zero</div>
                <div class="impact-metric-lbl">Paper-based certification</div>
              </article>
              <article class="impact-metric-card">
                <div class="impact-metric-num">Live</div>
                <div class="impact-metric-lbl">Digital certificate verification</div>
              </article>
            </div>
            <div class="impact-metrics-cta">
              <a class="btn btn-primary btn-glow btn-md" asp-page="/Contact"><span class="btn-glow-label">Discuss a Similar Project</span><svg class="btn-glow-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Other Government Projects — horizontal carousel -->
  <section class="other-projects">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="other-projects-head">
        <h2 class="other-projects-heading">Other Government Projects</h2>
        <div class="other-projects-nav" role="group" aria-label="Carousel navigation">
          <button type="button" class="other-projects-arrow" id="otherProjectsPrev" aria-label="Previous projects">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"/></svg>
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="other-projects-arrow" id="otherProjectsNext" aria-label="Next projects">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="other-projects-track" id="otherProjectsTrack">
        <article class="op-card op-card--green">
          <a asp-page="/CaseStudies/BeeStarLabel" class="op-card-banner" aria-label="BEE Star Label Compliance">
            <img src="/images/logos/gov/BEE Other project.png" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <div class="op-card-body">
            <h3 class="op-card-title">BEE Star Label Compliance</h3>
            <p class="op-card-desc">National platform replacing manual appliance compliance inspections with offline-first field officer app and real-time dashboards for State Designated Agencies.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="op-card op-card--mint">
          <a asp-page="/CaseStudies" class="op-card-banner" aria-label="Sickle Scan — National Health Screening">
            <img src="/images/logos/gov/Sickle Scan Other project.png" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <div class="op-card-body">
            <h3 class="op-card-title">Sickle Scan &mdash; National Health Screening Platform</h3>
            <p class="op-card-desc">Offline-capable, multilingual mobile platform deployed in tribal and remote areas for India&rsquo;s national sickle cell disease eradication initiative.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="op-card op-card--peach">
          <a asp-page="/CaseStudies/SansadCafeteria" class="op-card-banner" aria-label="Sansad Cafeteria Food Ordering System">
            <img src="/images/logos/gov/Parilament Other project (1).png" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <div class="op-card-body">
            <h3 class="op-card-title">Sansad Cafeteria Food Ordering System</h3>
            <p class="op-card-desc">Multi-outlet facility management system deployed across Parliament premises, serving Members of Parliament in one of India&rsquo;s highest-security environments.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="op-card op-card--blue">
          <a asp-page="/CaseStudies/Manthan" class="op-card-banner" aria-label="Manthan — Defence PSU Platform">
            <img src="/images/logos/gov/Manthan Other project.png" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <div class="op-card-body">
            <h3 class="op-card-title">Manthan &mdash; Defence PSU Platform</h3>
            <p class="op-card-desc">Enterprise technology platform for Munitions India Limited &mdash; secure, compliant digital infrastructure supporting a Defence Public Sector Undertaking.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="op-card op-card--red">
          <a asp-page="/CaseStudies" class="op-card-banner" aria-label="NBT India E-commerce">
            <img src="/images/logos/gov/NBT Other project.png.png" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <div class="op-card-body">
            <h3 class="op-card-title">National Book Trust E-commerce</h3>
            <p class="op-card-desc">Multilingual e-commerce platform for the Ministry of Education&rsquo;s National Book Trust &mdash; catalogue, payments and fulfilment for India&rsquo;s flagship publisher.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        
        <article class="op-card op-card--violet">
          <a asp-page="/CaseStudies" class="op-card-banner" aria-label="Parliamentary Affairs Portal">
            <img src="/images/case-studies/parliamentary-affairs.png" alt="" loading="lazy" />
          </a>
          <div class="op-card-body">
            <h3 class="op-card-title">Parliamentary Affairs Portal</h3>
            <p class="op-card-desc">Digital workflow platform for the Ministry of Parliamentary Affairs &mdash; legislative session tracking, document management and inter-ministry coordination.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
      
      <div class="other-projects-dots" id="otherProjectsDots" role="tablist" aria-label="Carousel pages">
        <button type="button" class="op-dot is-active" aria-label="Page 1"></button>
        <button type="button" class="op-dot" aria-label="Page 2"></button>
        <button type="button" class="op-dot" aria-label="Page 3"></button>
        <button type="button" class="op-dot" aria-label="Page 4"></button>
        <button type="button" class="op-dot" aria-label="Page 5"></button>
